channel.title: Socks 71
channel.description: In gateway arm monitor I have this warning : "socks version 71 not recognized" (tor is not http proxy). Is it some privacy problem? Thx

item.title: Socks 71
item.dc:creator: Patrick
item.description:
No privacy problem. Arm would most likely be not the right tool to detect those. This likely is caused by whonixcheck which checks if a Tor SocksPort is reachable (and it would report issues if it’s not).
